B.Qt=new A.a1("EET/LTAA0123 means the estimated elapsed time to the LTAA FIR boundary is 1 hour 23 minutes.","EET/LTAA0123, LTAA FIR s\u0131n\u0131r\u0131na tahmini ge\xe7i\u015f s\xfcresinin 1 saat 23 dakika oldu\u011fu anlam\u0131na gelir.","EET")
