B.Yz=new A.m(B.x,"SMS neden bilinmeli?","ICAO, SMS (Safety Management System) uygulamas\u0131n\u0131 zorunlu k\u0131lmaktad\u0131r. T\xfcm havac\u0131l\u0131k personeli SMS terminolojisini bilmeli; raporlama sistemlerine katk\u0131da bulunmal\u0131d\u0131r. S\u0131nav sorular\u0131nda da SMS kavramlar\u0131 giderek daha fazla yer almaktad\u0131r.",null,null,null)
B.a_w=new A.m(B.v,"\ud83d\udee1\ufe0f Temel SMS Terimleri","**Risk y\xf6netimi:**\n\u2022 **Hazard** \u2192 tehlike kayna\u011f\u0131 (risk olu\u015fturabilecek durum/nesne)\n\u2022 **Risk** \u2192 tehlikenin ger\xe7ekle\u015fme olas\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131 \xd7 sonucunun \u015fiddeti\n\u2022 **Severity** \u2192 \u015fiddet (sonucun ciddiyeti)\n\u2022 **Likelihood / Probability** \u2192 olas\u0131l\u0131k\n\u2022 **Mitigation** \u2192 azaltma (riski d\xfc\u015f\xfcrme \xf6nlemi)\n\u2022 **Residual risk** \u2192 kalan risk (\xf6nlem sonras\u0131)\n\n**Raporlama:**\n\u2022 **Occurrence** \u2192 olay (kaza veya kaza \xf6ncesi durum)\n\u2022 **Incident** \u2192 ciddi olmayan olay\n\u2022 **Serious incident** \u2192 kaza s\u0131n\u0131r\u0131na yak\u0131n olay\n\u2022 **Accident** \u2192 kaza (hasar/yaralanma var)\n\u2022 **Near miss / AIRPROX** \u2192 ramak kala\n\u2022 **Mandatory occurrence report (MOR)** \u2192 zorunlu olay raporu\n\u2022 **Just culture** \u2192 su\xe7lamadan \xf6te, sistemi iyile\u015ftirmeye odakl\u0131 k\xfclt\xfcr",null,null,null)
B.PD=new A.a1('"The hazard of bird strike was assessed with high severity and medium likelihood, resulting in a risk rating of HIGH."',"Ku\u015f \xe7arpmas\u0131 tehlikesi y\xfcksek \u015fiddet ve orta olas\u0131l\u0131kla de\u011ferlendirildi; risk derecesi Y\xdcKSEK.","hazard \u2026 severity \u2026 likelihood \u2026 risk rating")
B.OM=new A.a1('"Pilots are encouraged to file occurrence reports under the just culture framework without fear of punitive action."',"Pilotlar cezaland\u0131rma korkusu olmadan adaletli k\xfclt\xfcr \xe7er\xe7evesinde olay raporlar\u0131 doldurmaya te\u015fvik edilmektedir.","occurrence reports \u2026 just culture \u2026 without fear of punitive action")
